Dialogs.Dialog: 高嶺
There is fruit punch. Why is it called puch?
Oh, I thought the same. It's a strange name.
Right? I wonder why it's not called fruit compote.
Com..pote?
At home, I call it fruit compote...
Huh.
But in a coffe shop, fruit compote is called fruit punch.
I've been curious lately. Are you the same?
Not really... I don't eat that much, so I'm not sure.
I see. Yes, I'll remember it.
（What are you going to use that information for?）
高嶺
Is there anything alse you don't like besides fruit punch?
It's not that I don't like it, I just don't eat that much.
Then, what do you like?
You can't eat me.
▲高嶺＊＊▲, anything with you is delicious.
Oh you... But, I think so too. Except for bitter coffe.
I add sugar to it. About 10 dozen.
That's too sweet.
Well then, I'll add salt too.
Now, that's just weird.
高嶺
Come to think of it, do you want to put salt in your coffe?
Huh?
What other unusual drinks are you drinking?
It was a joke... But, I used to drink chili sauce a long time ago.
Oh, nice. Do you love chili sauce?
I didn't liked it. I mistakenly tought it was tomato juice...
Was it next to the tomato juice? The same as papa.
What do you mean?
Papa confused chili sauce as tomato juice.
Huh, I think I'll try it next time.
Fufu, when you meet papa someday, can I tell him what you think?
It was a surprising use of chili sauce and I tried it an a mackerel can.
高嶺
How was it?
It was pretty delicious.
How does it taste?
It was like mackerel muniel. It had a strong sour-flavor.
I guess it's a lemon substitute.
Eh... Well, if you say so, that sounds right.
Fufu, why don't you try lemons next time?
... I will do that.
高嶺
Hey, you live alone, right?
Hmm? Yeah.
Do you do your housework properly?
Well, in its own way. I'm doing it... well?
Really?
It's okay. I'm doing it properly.
Then it's fine.
I wonder if it's so dangerous.
That's not the case... I'm worried about you.
（I don't know...）
高嶺
Hey, it's about the housework.
Oh, I'm doing it properly.
Also the cleaning? Are the rooms clean?
▲高嶺＊＊▲, it might not look so... from your point of view.
I'm getting worried...
I think it's okay, though. I know where things are, and there are no cockroaches...
Kya!
Hmm?
N-nothing...
（You don't like them, do you...）
高嶺
If I'm persistent, would you forgive me?
Hmm?
About the housework...
Oh, I know you care so much.
How about washing?
I try to do it sometimes, but...
Huh, you don't do it everyday?
Almost... every day. It's just me, so it's not that much.
Hmm...
（You don't have to worry that much...）
高嶺
Hey, I was thinking...
What?
I think I should help you with your housework.
Huh,▲高嶺＊＊▲ wants to help!?
... I knew it, can't I?
I don't hate it, but... I think it's not good. And your parents would worry.
Why would mama and papa worry?
I don't know why... I'm just sure.
I'll ask you if you really need me, so it's all good.
Yes... I'll keep it in mind for the future, okay?
（Then... are you looking for it?）
高嶺
... I'd like to talk to you about fish dishes.
Cooking... I wonder if I'll be useful. Otherwise, I'll be glad.
Yes, thank you. I tried to judge the fish...
Was it alive?
No, not really. The fish lying on the cutting board seems to be staring at me.
Yes, I'm sure. It's a little scary when you meet the fish at the supermarket.
When I looked into its eyes, I couldn't point my kitchen knife at all...
Close you eyes... but it would be impossible or dangerous.
What should I do?
It's not a cooking problem. Hmm...
Hmm...
It's about the fish dish you mentioned before.
高嶺
Yes.
In other words, are you afraid of the fish's eyes?
It's not the eyes themselves, but I can seem to hear its voice...
Voice... from the fish?
"What are you doing?", "What are you doing to me?"... That kind of voice.
You can't actually hear it, can you?
Of course. Doens't happen to you? I even hear stuffed animals.
I don't have stuffed animals in my room...
It feels like the stuffed bunny will say "Welcome back", "Did you have fun?". I can hear things like that.
I'm not affaid of that.
Of course.
It's about the fish dishes.
高嶺
Yes, isn't there a good way?
Why don't you turn your face when you buy it?
If that's the case, I can't see how fresh it is... And it's not a fundamental solution.
Why don't you wear sunglasess and cook? You won't even see the eyes of the fish.
Then I would look like a weird person.
Paint the fish's eyes. Even magic paint is good.
That would be a little cruel...
But they are already dead.
Even so... it's not good.
Well, that's right...
About the problem of cooking fish.
高嶺
Yes.
You should hide the eyes of the fish, cover them with a cloth.
I've already done it, but I can still feel them. Those eyes under the cloth... gazing.
Then... I have it!
What's wrong?
I will scold it. Don't complain to▲高嶺＊＊▲!
The fish...?
That's right, don't scare other people's girlfriends!
The fish fot angry... That's why I can eat it.
...That's right!
I feel a little pity for it. But... okay.
I will cook while thinking you are on my side. If I can do that, I will be fine.
高嶺
There's something I'd like to tell you.
What?
I often don't understand the words everyone uses...
Sometimes I miss myself in the conversation.
Ah, I see. It's okay, I know some words.
Thank you. Then... what is "Gachi"?
"Gachi" is...
How do you write its kanji?
...Kanji?
A fair game, seriously... I understand the meaning, but I don't understand the kanji.
Gachi, uh... "Ga" means I, and "chi" means... blood?
I see! That's great, thank you.
...I'm sorry,▲高嶺＊＊▲. It was a joke...
高嶺
You know, there's another popular word I don't understand...
What kind?
What does women's power mean?
Well,▲高嶺＊＊▲ has high girl power.
My friend told me, is that a good thing?
Of course, it's expensive.
Then, are you high on male power?
...I wonder. It's different from boyfriend's power.
Whatever!
... It's weird.
高嶺
Hey. What kind of person is "Pane"?
Marzipan.
Yes, that's the one. I really understand what it means. I think it should be called Pa nee-san.
I don't think "Pa nee-san" is correct.
You don't have to laugh so much...
Sorry, sorry.
You mean... it isn't about people?
It might be a person.
Oh, is that right?
It may not be a person.
Eh... Oh, come on! I'm messing around with you.
Ha ha.
高嶺
There are also words that I don't understand. When do you use "Disuru"?
▲高嶺＊＊▲, I don't want to be dissed.
THIS can be done? THIS is passive? I wonder what it means...
No, no. It's not "This", but "Dis".
Oh, then that's a bad thing.
Was it originally a rapper term?
Rap? Is it a music term?
Well...
Well, I'll see you later...
（This thing is one of you good points,▲高嶺＊＊▲）
